WEBVTT

00:05.193 --> 00:09.586
Oh, good morning little friends,
your singing is oh so pretty.

00:10.246 --> 00:12.326
Yes, it is a very
beautiful day today,

00:12.653 --> 00:14.826
certainly something
worth singing about.

00:15.353 --> 00:19.293
♪ There's music in the treetops
and there's music in the vale. ♪

00:19.626 --> 00:23.460
<i>♪ and all around me</i>
<i>music fills the sky ♪</i>

00:23.966 --> 00:25.866
<i>♪ There's music by the river </i>

00:26.006 --> 00:28.060
<i>♪ and there's music</i>
<i>in the grass ♪</i>

00:28.193 --> 00:32.393
<i>♪ And the music makes your</i>
<i>heart soar in reply ♪</i>

00:32.826 --> 00:35.273
<i>♪ Aahhhh! </i>

00:36.387 --> 00:41.068
<i>♪ Aaaaahhh! </i>

00:41.475 --> 00:43.526
<i>♪ Ah ha ha! Ah ha ha! </i>

00:43.596 --> 00:45.734
<i>♪ Aaaaah! </i>

