slice of heaven.

02:06.793 --> 02:08.633
With ice cream on top!

02:09.212 --> 02:12.912
Fluttershy, I cannot believe
your spectacular voice

02:12.947 --> 02:15.228
isn't part of the
Pony Tones Quartet!

02:15.782 --> 02:17.622
Um...well...I...

02:17.676 --> 02:19.408
Especially since you're
having us perform

02:19.433 --> 02:22.019
for your Ponyville Pet Center
Fundraiser tomorrow night!

02:22.803 --> 02:24.934
Well, you see, I...

02:25.014 --> 02:27.219
This simply must be rectified!

02:27.430 --> 02:29.824
You must share that
stunning voice at the event.

02:29.913 --> 02:31.936
Yeah! It will be so amazing!

02:32.153 --> 02:34.793
