a shining star...

02:38.220 --> 02:40.979
<i>With everypony staring</i>
<i>at you, judging you,</i>

02:41.024 --> 02:43.529
jealously noting how they
could be WAY better than you.

02:43.539 --> 02:45.632
Why wasn't it them?
Why wasn't it them?

02:45.737 --> 02:48.035
<i>And then, when you choke,</i>
<i>they'll turn on you</i>

02:48.044 --> 02:49.660
becoming a seething angry mob

02:49.830 --> 02:51.388
and you'll be horribly
humiliated,

02:51.644 --> 02:54.582
never able to show your
face in Ponyville again!

02:54.729 --> 02:58.393
Pinkie Pie! Don't
be ridiculous!

02:59.337 --> 03:00.700
