03:01.792 --> 03:02.844
Come, Fluttershy.

03:02.988 --> 03:06.025
You will join the group making
the Pony Tones Quartet

03:06.313 --> 03:08.112
the Pony Tones Quintet!

03:08.662 --> 03:09.360
No!

03:09.971 --> 03:11.024
Pardon me?

03:11.523 --> 03:13.174
I love the Pony Tones.

03:13.414 --> 03:14.934
I'm one of their biggest fans.

03:15.280 --> 03:17.424
But I do not want to
perform with them.

03:17.907 --> 03:19.286
Why not, Fluttershy?

03:19.635 --> 03:26.729
Well you see, I...I
have...um...I-I have...

03:26.918 --> 03:27.644
