03:32.598 --> 03:33.692
Is it contagious?

03:34.099 --> 03:36.297
Stage fright isn't
a disease, Pinkie.

03:36.646 --> 03:38.806
It just means that Fluttershy
is scared to perform

03:38.819 --> 03:39.884
in front of everypony.

03:40.288 --> 03:42.016
