05:18.265 --> 05:19.180
Sounds great!

05:19.846 --> 05:22.793
Oh, Rarity, the Pony Tones
are really going to make

05:22.803 --> 05:25.747
the Ponyville Pet Center
Fundraiser so special!

05:26.054 --> 05:29.472
Thank you so much for
helping me help the animals!

05:29.513 --> 05:32.665
Oh yes. It is wonderful
when a plan comes together

05:32.678 --> 05:34.822
without any sort of
drama, isn't it?

05:55.910 --> 05:57.100
Morning, Fluttershy.

05:57.472 --> 05:59.331
Good morning,
Pony Tones!

05:59.574 --> 06:02.819
Actually, we're the Pony
Tones minus one tone.

06:03.056 --> 06:05.392
Big Mac is
inconveniently late.

06:11.923 --> 06:12.985
Well, there you are!

06:13.228 --> 06:15.062
Have I not told you
about punctuality?

06:15.513 --> 06:17.456
Ah! I don't want
to hear it!

06:29.904 --> 06:32.422
