start the song?

06:34.179 --> 06:35.292
Nnope.

06:35.577 --> 06:36.214
Big Mac!

06:36.576 --> 06:37.664
Did you lose your voice?

06:38.496 --> 06:39.536
Eeyup.

06:45.987 --> 06:48.380
Whatever did you
do to cause this?

06:48.709 --> 06:50.041
Well...

06:51.977 --> 06:53.161
Howdy, everypony!

06:53.299 --> 06:56.521
And welcome to the 12th Annual
Ponyville Turkey Call!

07:00.320 --> 07:01.708
Who will take the
title this year?

07:02.009 --> 07:03.251
Will it be somepony new?

07:03.475 --> 07:06.710
