champion of six years

07:06.720 --> 07:10.672
<i>defend his title to make</i>
<i>it lucky number seven?</i>

07:11.270 --> 07:13.715
We'll find out if
ya stop yer gabbin'

07:13.720 --> 07:16.034
and git on with
the gobblin'!

07:16.172 --> 07:17.507
All right, everypony!

07:17.852 --> 07:19.203
Let's talk turkey!

07:19.654 --> 07:21.459
Big Mac, yer up!

07:25.211 --> 07:27.979
A Turkey Call?

07:28.124 --> 07:31.577
