all the music

07:52.500 --> 07:53.673
and we just don't have time.

07:53.945 --> 07:56.073
<i>I'm sorry, Fluttershy,</i>
<i>but I have no remedy</i>

07:56.083 --> 07:57.094
<i>for this situation.</i>

07:58.937 --> 07:59.977
Of course!

08:00.195 --> 08:01.001
A remedy!

08:01.289 --> 08:02.060
Follow me!

08:08.438 --> 08:11.244
<i>Ahhhh!</i>

08:11.292 --> 08:12.192
Hmmm.

08:12.451 --> 08:14.336
Aaahh.

08:16.358 --> 08:18.835
I can cure this
pony that is hoarse,

08:18.999 --> 08:21.700
but it will take
a longer course.

08:22.240 --> 08:22.979
Come again?

08:23.260 --> 08:23.846
Hmmm.

08:24.201 --> 08:26.672
