17:48.666 --> 17:50.413
singing in front of everypony!

17:50.553 --> 17:52.480
And, you know, I don't think
any pony was jealous

17:52.573 --> 17:54.853
cause there certainly
wasn't an angry mob!

17:55.033 --> 17:57.300
But it must have been horrible
standing there on stage!

17:57.400 --> 18:00.040
All eyes glued directly on you.

18:00.113 --> 18:03.293
It's like you were living your
own personal worst nightmare!

18:05.546 --> 18:06.493
It was!

18:11.380 --> 18:12.973
What? Too much?

18:14.920 --> 18:17.720
What Pinkie meant to say was
that you were really great.

18:18.173 --> 18:20.026
Wait! Didn't I say that?

18:20.253 --> 18:21.273
Hardly!

18:21.613 --> 18:22.113
Whoops!

18:22.180 --> 18:24.160
YOU WERE GREAT!

18:24.446 --> 18:27.133
You totally blew
my mind!

18:28.060 --> 18:29.440
Incredible!

18:30.893 --> 18:34.753
Though, no offence, you
kind of sounded like a dude.

18:36.926 --> 18:39.486
A great sounding dude!

18:42.780 --> 18:44.560
Well, thank you all.

18:44.926 --> 18:46.300
I'm glad you enjoyed it...

18:48.646 --> 18:51.313
...because I'm never going to
sing in front of anypony

18:51.426 --> 18:52.500
ever again.

18:53.726 --> 18:54.340
Oh no!

18:54.446 --> 18:55.480
Are you kidding me?

18:55.760 --> 18:57.940
Can we please
stop running!

19:01.340 --> 19:04.440
I just don't understand
why, Fluttershy.

19:04.666 --> 19:07.260
<i>After all, you're the one</i>
<i>that wanted the Pony Tones</i>

19:07.273 --> 19:10.346
to sing for every silly
thing that was requested of us.

19:10.640 --> 19:13.593
You mean, you knew I
really wanted to perform?

19:13.993 --> 19:15.500
Of course I knew!

19:16.093 --> 19:16.926
Oh.

19:17.306 --> 19:20.666
And for all her babbling, Pinkie
Pie was right about one thing.

19:21.140 --> 19:22.140
Only one?

19:22.833 --> 19:26.426
When that curtain fell, and
everypony saw you singing,

19:26.620 --> 19:29.073
you lived your worst nightmare.

19:29.686 --> 19:30.760
Was it really that bad?

19:31.446 --> 19:32.386
Yes!

19:32.626 --> 19:34.533
Well, what was so bad about it?

19:34.840 --> 19:36.346
The thunderous
applause?

19:36.653 --> 19:38.493
The praise for your
fantastic singin'?

19:38.706 --> 19:41.453
The SCREAMING FANS?

19:50.266 --> 19:54.320
♪ There's music in the treetops
and there's music in the vale ♪

19:54.613 --> 19:58.686
<i>♪ and all around the</i>
<i>music fills the sky. ♪</i>

19:58.920 --> 20:02.873
♪ There's music by the river and
<i>there's music in the grass. ♪</i>

20:03.326 --> 20:07.493
<i>♪ And the music makes your</i>
<i>heart soar into flight. ♪</i>

20:07.506 --> 20:10.466
<i>When you find you've</i>
<i>got the music,</i>

20:10.473 --> 20:12.806
<i>♪ You've got to look</i>
<i>inside and find. ♪</i>

20:12.813 --> 20:14.760
<i>♪ Find you've got the music </i>

20:14.773 --> 20:16.980
<i>♪ The music deep inside you. </i>

20:16.993 --> 20:19.126
<i>♪ Find you've got the music. </i>

20:19.140 --> 20:22.093
<i>♪ Cause when you look</i>
<i>inside you'll see it. ♪</i>

20:23.500 --> 20:27.660
<i>♪ You're going to find,</i>
<i>you're going to find. ♪</i>

20:27.740 --> 20:31.926
<i>♪ Got the music, got</i>
<i>the music...in you! ♪</i>

20:38.100 --> 20:39.693
You did it,
Fluttershy!

20:40.086 --> 20:41.746
See? That
wasn't so bad.

20:42.040 --> 20:44.146
And you didn't look completely
petrified by the fact

20:44.153 --> 20:45.800
that we're all staring
at you at all!

20:48.100 --> 20:49.153
How do you feel?

20:49.420 --> 20:51.766
Surprisingly OK!

20:52.246 --> 20:52.993
<i>Fantastic!</i>

20:53.400 --> 20:55.706
Because the Pony Tones
have been booked for the

20:55.713 --> 20:58.826
Apple Family's Zap Apple
Jam Extraordinaire!

20:59.133 --> 21:02.013
Oh no! I couldn't
do that!

21:04.386 --> 21:06.346
Why not?
How come?
Seriously?

21:06.913 --> 21:08.353
I'll get there someday.

21:08.600 --> 21:11.000
But for now, baby
steps, everypony.

21:11.293 --> 21:12.260
Baby steps.

21:14.306 --> 21:17.206
<i>Sometimes being</i>
<i>afraid can stop you</i>

21:17.253 --> 21:19.193
<i>from doing something</i>
<i>that you love.</i>

21:19.693 --> 21:22.246
<i>But hiding behind these fears</i>
<i>means you're only hiding</i>

21:22.253 --> 21:23.520
<i>from your true self.</i>

21:24.133 --> 21:26.373
<i>It's much better to</i>
<i>face those fears</i>

21:26.586 --> 21:31.120
so you can shine and be the best
<i>pony you can possibly be!</i>
